COMPANY INFORMATION

The Threadneedle group of companies ("Threadneedle") comprises
those companies whose holding company is Threadneedle Asset
Management Holdings Sàrl. References to Columbia Threadneedle
Investments are to companies in the Columbia and Threadneedle group
of companies.
